{"tid":1720991,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"重拾教鞭！亨利任蒙特利爾衝擊教練","createTime":"2019-11-14T14:00:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T16:44:34.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e925800435b01c91e9513aa6823e9741a5522193","tid":1720991,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:00:40.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】昔日著名法國射手亨利，周四落實出任美職聯蒙特利爾衝擊的新教練。<br />\n<br />\n亨利（Thierry Henry）接受新球會訪問時表示：「能成為蒙特利爾衝擊的教練，並重返美職聯，這是我的榮幸。美職聯是我非常了解的聯賽，亦曾在此度過美好的時光。由魁北克開始，蒙特利爾有著巨大的多元化文化遺產，我一直都很關注蒙特利爾衝擊這支球隊，現在終加入他們。」亨利與衝擊簽約兩年，直至2021年球季，合同當中亦有續約多1年的條款。<br />\n<br />\n亨利2010年由巴塞隆拿轉戰美職聯，效力紐約紅牛4年半後，2014年12月正式離開，並在當月同時宣佈掛靴。退役後亨利曾擔任足球評述員，2016至18年亦出任過比利時國家隊助教，直至2018年10月得到法甲球會摩納哥的賞識，首嘗領隊滋味，可惜只是短短執教20場，就因錄得4勝5和11負的劣績而被辭退，直至周四終落實再當教練。<br />\n<br />\n亨利在美職聯效力的4年半，合共為紐約紅牛上陣122場，攻入51球，兼交出42次助攻。他亦曾3度當選美職聯最佳11人，以及4度出席美職聯明星賽。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : Twitter圖片"},{"pid":"3856c37a41b59e98899cf434dc4745c88a1f0162","tid":1720991,"uid":190793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:01:28.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n［韓國戰線］青瓦台請願聯署 同我簽爆佢 （教學）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1720736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1720736</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1aaa951bbe572fda3c131ddab4a9cb836f12a2bb","tid":1720991,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:01:40.000Z","msg":"同師父雲加一齊出黎害人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7af54eab3d50b501c36d36e949d43f643f08d979","tid":1720991,"uid":206337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:02:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55bbf16a1f3ddfa96e99ef93ec16246f686398f2","tid":1720991,"uid":185092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:02:14.000Z","msg":"教長過三個月已經當你贏"},{"pid":"4ced7b66e67c0a066ccc91f72d586ea4ecd3fab2","tid":1720991,"uid":81273,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:23:16.000Z","msg":"我一直都很關注蒙特利爾衝擊這支球隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dff357408b90538d0df1f8b394f7425a26a20eb","tid":1720991,"uid":20473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ced7b66e67c0a066ccc91f72d586ea4ecd3fab2","tid":1720991,"uid":81273,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:23:16.000Z","msg":"我一直都很關注蒙特利爾衝擊這支球隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:35:24.000Z","msg":"關注好重要架"},{"pid":"d8b759e5b106c1e82cf2c993df1fd22fcf5aa437","tid":1720991,"uid":310469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:44:34.000Z","msg":"美職都唔放過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}